title: Hounds of Zaroff 1932 - When Humans Become Prey: The Ultimate Survival Test

sources.title: Hounds of Zaroff 1932 - When Humans Become Prey: The Ultimate Survival Test
sources.description:
After shipwrecked hunter Bob Rainsford washes up at Count Zaroff’s island fortress, he discovers the aristocrat’s lethal hobby: hunting humans as "the most dangerous game." With fellow survivor Eve Trowbridge, Bob must outwit Zaroff’s hounds and traps in a deadly round of outdoor chess—where losing means checkmate.

Original title: The Most Dangerous Game (1932)

Directed by Ernest B. Schoedsack & Irving Pichel

Main cast:
Joel McCrea - Bob Rainsford
Fay Wray - Eve Trowbridge
Leslie Banks - Count Zaroff 
Robert Armstrong - Martin Trowbridge 
Noble Johnson - Ivan 
Genres: Action, Adventure, Horror, Thriller 

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/N8_tUB_M0FE
